{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSMediaRule","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriétés</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule/media\"><code>media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Héritage&nbsp;:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Pages liées à CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>L'interface <strong><code>CSSMediaRule</code></strong> représente une seule règle CSS <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/CSS/@media\"><code>@media</code></a>. Elle met en œuvre l'interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, et donc l'interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> et l'interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> avec une valeur de type <code>4</code> (<code>CSSRule.MEDIA_RULE</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<p>La syntaxe est décrite en utilisant le format <a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/WebIDL/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebIDL</a>.</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">interface CSSMediaRule : CSSConditionRule {\n    readonly attribute MediaList media;\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriétés","title":"Propriétés","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En tant que <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, et donc à la fois <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> et <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <code>CSSMediaRule</code> implémente également les propriétés de ces interfaces. Elle a la propriété spécifique suivante :</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssmediarule.media_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule/media\"><code>CSSMediaRule.media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Cette valeur ne peut pas être changée.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Lecture seule </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Spécifie un <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaList\"><code>MediaList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> représentant le support de destination prévu pour les informations de style.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"méthodes","title":"Méthodes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En tant que <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, et donc à la fois <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> et <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <code>CSSMediaRule</code> met également en œuvre les méthodes de cette interface. Elle n'a pas de méthodes spécifiques.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/#the-cssmediarule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'CSSMediaRule' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidat au statut de recommandation</span></td>\n      <td>Dérivé de la règle <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-cssmediarule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'CSSMediaRule' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Version de travail</span></td>\n      <td>Aucun changement par rapport à <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La spécificaction 'Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification'\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSMediaRule\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'CSSMediaRule' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSMediaRule","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntaxe","id":"syntaxe"},{"text":"Propriétés","id":"propriétés"},{"text":"Méthodes","id":"méthodes"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"}],"summary":"L'interface CSSMediaRule représente une seule règle CSS @media. Elle met en œuvre l'interface CSSConditionRule (en-US), et donc l'interface CSSGroupingRule (en-US) et l'interface CSSRule (en-US) avec une valeur de type 4 (CSSRule.MEDIA_RULE).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/cssmediarule","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/cssmediarule/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule","title":"CSSMediaRule"}],"pageTitle":"CSSMediaRule - Référence Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}